OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,FViolence against women and girls in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland was the main issue
OL,9,Fdiscussed by the Executive on
OL,10,FThursday, health minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FMr Nesbitt said he was considering
OL,14,Fwhether a summit could be organised to
OL,15,Fengage with communities on the issue
OL,16,Fof domestic violence against women and
OL,17,Fgirls, but warned the problem would
OL,18,Fnot "go away quickly".
OL,26,@zD@EOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
