OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,FHe also said funding was not withdrawn
OL,8,Ffrom Women's Aid, but instead their
OL,9,Fapplication was refused; and added
OL,10,Fthat he would prefer if they were
OL,11,Freceiving funding from his department.
OL,13,FThe topic of violence against women
OL,14,Fand girls has come to the fore after
OL,15,Fthe murder of two women this month as
OL,16,Fwell as the conviction of Stephen
OL,17,FMcCullagh for the murder of his
OL,18,Fpregnant partner, Natalie McNally.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,FA murder investigations is ongoing
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of Amy Doherty in
OL,9,FLondonderry at the weekend, while a
OL,10,Fman has appeared in court charged with
OL,11,Fthe murder of Ellie Flanagan in
OL,12,FFermanagh earlier this month.
OL,14,FAppearing before the health committee
OL,15,Fon Thursday, Mr Nesbitt said funding
OL,16,Ffor Women's Aid had not been cut, but
OL,17,Finstead they had not qualified for
OL,18,Ffunding.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,FHe was responding to a question from
OL,8,Fcommittee chairperson Philip McGuigan,
OL,9,Fwho said the Department of Health cut
OL,10,Fits funding in 2023 by half and
OL,11,F"withdrew completely" core grant
OL,12,Ffunding in 2024.
OL,14,FMr Nesbitt said: "If you're referring
OL,15,Fto core funding, we did not cut this
OL,16,Ftime. We didn't cut them out.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@UO]vD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,F"We redesigned the scheme two years
OL,8,Fago, we redesigned it again for this
OL,9,Fcoming year because it had been around
OL,10,Ffor over 20 years and new charities
OL,11,Fcouldn't even apply for it.
OL,13,F"So, what happened was, Women's Aid
OL,14,Fdidn't meet the criteria to get it and
OL,15,FI think that's a very important
OL,16,Fdistinction between us actively
OL,17,Fdeciding to withdraw their funding and
OL,18,Fthem being unsuccessful in the
OL,19,Fapplication.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,F"I would much rather they were
OL,8,Freceiving core grant funding from the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health, and that's why
OL,10,Fwe provide feedback to unsuccessful
OL,11,Fapplicants."
OL,13,FAsked if he could look to see if more
OL,14,Fcould be done for Women's Aid, Mr
OL,15,FNesbitt replied: "I will certainly do
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,18,F"But we are talking about governance,
OL,19,Fand we have to have governance
OL,20,Fstructures about how we distribute the
OL,21,Fmoney."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@LO]wD@ROUzD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,FHe added: "I've come to you from an
OL,8,FExecutive meeting that started at 10am
OL,9,Fand is still ongoing, and I hope I
OL,10,Fwill be forgiven if I'm breaking
OL,11,Fconfidence by saying the substantive
OL,12,Fdiscussion this morning was on the
OL,13,Fviolence against women and girls and
OL,14,Fthe two deeply regrettable, tragic
OL,15,Fmurders."
OL,17,FHe said he planned to write to First
OL,18,FMinister Michelle O'Neill and deputy
OL,19,FFirst Minister Emma Little-Pengelly
OL,20,Fabout a proposal to "better" engage
OL,21,Fwith the community.
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@IO]|D@UOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,F"I also think it's probably one of
OL,8,Fthose issues that's going to be a
OL,9,Fgenerational transformation.
OL,11,F"So, what I'm thinking about is not
OL,12,Fjust Women's Aid, but all the
OL,13,Fcommunity and voluntary groups that
OL,14,Fthe Department of Health funds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774552271
OL,3,CProblem won't 'go away quickly' says
OL,4,CNesbitt on violence against women and
OL,5,Cgirls
OL,7,F"So, the ones who are maybe dealing
OL,8,Fwith women's issues, and particularly
OL,9,Fwith youth, could we pull them all in
OL,10,Fsomewhere... could we just have a
OL,11,Fsummit and say we've got to get out
OL,12,Fand start messaging and really engage
OL,13,Fthe community in what's going on. It's
OL,14,Fnot going to go away quickly."
